Comment: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Comment: 0,0:00:42.03,0:00:42.75,orig,,0,0,0,,Stick with your close range weapons!
Comment: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:09.75,orig,,0,0,0,,but the goblins might be stronger than us.
Comment: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.35,orig,,0,0,0,,How many of us are there?
Comment: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:48.30,orig,,0,0,0,,It looks almost like a castle rather than a town.
Comment: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:04.80,orig,,0,0,0,,Familiar or not, I can't remember anybody...
Comment: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:20.60,orig,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, does anybody know where we are?
Comment: 0,0:08:52.50,0:09:00.65,orig,,0,0,0,,You can call me Chief. Or Bri, but only if you say it affectionately.
Comment: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:02.40,orig,,0,0,0,,Give us answers.
Comment: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:28.73,orig,,0,0,0,,You wanna find out for yourself?
Comment: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:34.40,orig,,0,0,0,,In time.
Comment: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:37.50,orig,,0,0,0,,And then I'll get you good.
Comment: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:51.60,orig,,0,0,0,,You should be able to live off of it for the time being.
Comment: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:55.95,orig,,0,0,0,,I don't have my cell phone either.
Comment: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:45.20,orig,,0,0,0,,I adore fast learners.
Comment: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:40.95,orig,,0,0,0,,We spent eight silvers to join a guild, so we each have two silvers left.
Comment: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:42.85,orig,,0,0,0,,One silver equals one hundred coppers...
Comment: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:48.50,orig,,0,0,0,,so even if we use the minimum for living expenses, we'll only last about two weeks.
Comment: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:08.00,orig,,0,0,0,,You should feel honored.
Comment: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:55.57,orig,,0,0,0,,This is great to watch, you hear?
Comment: 0,0:19:56.05,0:19:58.40,orig,,0,0,0,,Keep going!
Comment: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:17.35,orig,,0,0,0,,Of course.

Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck are you doing, Haruhiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.30,0:00:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Get 'em and stab! Stick 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that easy! It's not like you're—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.70,0:00:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.15,0:00:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll hit allies with arrows if this turns into a melee!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.90,0:00:42.75,fix,,0,0,0,,Use swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma-Marque, Em—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.65,0:01:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Parc.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.90,0:01:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.90,0:01:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.05,0:01:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll heal you, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.70,0:01:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,O light, return to Lumiaris' divine protection. Cure!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.80,0:01:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a battle of life or death!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.05,0:01:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Both us and the goblins are fighting a real battle for our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't get more serious than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.95,0:01:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No living thing wants to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:50.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,We're all out of breath, even though\Nwe haven't exerted ourselves much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.90,0:01:52.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't goblins the weakest monsters in Grimgar?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.40,0:02:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're supposed to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:03.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,I don't want to admit it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.45,0:02:07.50,fix_it,,0,0,0,,...but the goblins...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:09.80,fix_it,,0,0,0,,...might be stronger than us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:33.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,Awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:42.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,Awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.05,0:02:49.65,Italics,,0,0,0,,Awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you gonna sleep, Haruhiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun's high.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you forgetting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Cock-a-doodle-doo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.15,0:03:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the sleepy eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was born with eyes like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean I'm sleepy, I've told you before!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar, no doubt you're still sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you both get dressed, will you come to the courtyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.60,0:03:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on breakfast duty...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I switched with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You seemed pretty tired from yesterday's fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that, Manato.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't seem that sorry, Haruhiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.35,0:04:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you on duty, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,When I woke up Moguzo had traded with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you can still harp on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't get up, I won't get my morning grub.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's starting to smell mighty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I enjoy cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I rather enjoy taste-testing, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yume, Moguzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I gathered these on our way back yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Will these work as additional ingredients?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Shihoru, I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a little under-salted?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Salt's also pretty pricey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:05:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try to be frugal until we're able to earn money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, we haven't even defeated one monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruhiro and Ranta, are you both okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My Light Magic can heal wounds,\Nbut it won't replenish lost blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No problems here. I'm fit as a fiddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I get a little dizzy, but I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we try the forest today again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We were against two goblins yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.65,0:05:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That might be too hard for us right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try going for a loner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll take too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If we keep running, it'll take forever\Nto accumulate my first Vices.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Renji and his group are moving ahead without hiccups, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better than overdoing it and getting hurt like yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A game?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.80,0:06:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Manato, what's a "game?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I... don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just used that word, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt like the right thing at the time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Game..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:17.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,Things like this happen to us sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:23.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,We impulsively use words that seem familiar,\Nbut we don't know the meaning of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:30.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,It makes us uneasy, like when something gets a\Nlittle stuck in your throat and you can't get it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:35.09,Italics,,0,0,0,,When I first came to the world of Grimgar...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:39.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't actually know where I came from either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:44.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'll tell you about my oldest memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:48.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,It was actually only from a couple of days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.25,0:06:53.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,Awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:07:01.30,Italics,,0,0,0,,I can't remember anything from before this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:04.45,Italics,,0,0,0,,I didn't know why I was here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:06.65,Italics,,0,0,0,,...how long I'd be here for...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:09.15,Italics,,0,0,0,,...or how long I'd been here already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anybody there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.35,fix,,0,0,0,,How many of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's count?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, no one here knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That over there... you think it's a town?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:45.80,fix,,0,0,0,,Rather than a town...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:48.30,fix,,0,0,0,,...it looks almost like a castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see any familiar faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No... nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:00.60,fix_it,,0,0,0,,Rather than familiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:03.15,fix_it,,0,0,0,,This is odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:04.80,fix_it,,0,0,0,,I can't remember anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:09.05,Italics,,0,0,0,,Not my friends, family, anybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.75,0:08:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where... is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:17.40,fix,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, does anybody know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:18.90,fix,,0,0,0,,Where...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:20.60,fix,,0,0,0,,....we are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We can ask them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, we can ask those guys wearing all that armor stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Grimgar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the town of Ortana.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to give you a warm welcome, my kittens.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The name's Brittany.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm chief and host of the Red Moon office of the\NVolunteer Soldier Squad for Ortana's Borderland Brigade.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:55.80,fix,,0,0,0,,Calling me Chief if fine and all, but Bri-chan is okay too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:09:00.65,fix,,0,0,0,,However in that case you better say it veeery affectionately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.65,0:09:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:02.40,fix,,0,0,0,,Answer my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck are the Borderland Brigade\Nand the Volunteer Soldier Squad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Demanding are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind ones like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.75,0:09:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Renji.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't like pervy guys like you—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Renji, let me tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No one has called me "perverted" and lived long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:27.95,fix,,0,0,0,,Wanna try?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:32.95,fix,,0,0,0,,Well, try and get me if you can, Pervy Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:34.40,fix,,0,0,0,,When time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:37.55,fix,,0,0,0,,I'll get you good, I'll get you very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.15,0:09:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to forget me after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.95,0:09:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten silver coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There are ten silvers in here per person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give a bag to those who join the Volunteer Soldier Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.05,0:09:51.65,fix,,0,0,0,,It should be enough for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, money...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:55.95,fix,,0,0,0,,No phone either...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:09:58.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,Phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:01.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,Huh, what's a "cell phone?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is proof that you're a trainee, priced at twenty silver coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,For twenty more, you can buy an official\Nbadge that comes with its own benefits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.45,0:10:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to buy them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, if you're not strong enough, you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:22.05,Italics,,0,0,0,,Die? I didn't realize this conversation was so serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What, exactly, do we need to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear Renji, you disappoint me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll defeat enemies by gathering information\Nwith your own wits and discernment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way of a Volunteer Soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So basically, we need to find out things\Nand think for ourselves for everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:45.30,fix,,0,0,0,,I love such fast learners.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,After you defeat a monster, take all the spoils and sell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,These are basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think that there are other types of menial labor to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a different story if you want to become a little pet of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:11:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Living has its own challenges.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you just one piece of advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, when you die, you die, but if you\Ngive up, you're definitely going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.55,0:11:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That, I am sure of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting today, you are all Volunteer Soldier trainees.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.15,0:11:42.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,In the borderlands of this world called Grimgar...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:47.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,...there are many other races and monsters\Nthat are hostile towards humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:52.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,The Borderland Brigade's mission is\Nto clear them out and suppress them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:12:00.45,Italics,,0,0,0,,But in reality, the regular army has their hands full\Nwith maintaining Ortana and the forts on the front line.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:04.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,So that's why Volunteer Soldiers like us are needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:08.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,Well, we're still trainees, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:15.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,Renji and his party have already bought\Nofficial Borderland Brigade badges from Bri-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:21.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,It seems you can trade monster items\Nlike horns and claws for a high price.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:26.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,Twenty silvers still seem pretty expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Meat! I want some meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Some hearty stuff that I can sink my teeth into!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They cost four coppers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Be patient until we can actually earn our living.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.20,0:12:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You just wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna eat everything in sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll clean out the stands, bones and all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you should eat the bones...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Or the stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat the small stuff, you'll only tire yourself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, I'm getting\Nmore tired just talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes you so useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No good. No good for anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're strong, Ranta?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't look it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}am{\i0} strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when I was a babe, I was famous for my hidden strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were famous for it, there was nothing hidden about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:29.30,Italics,,0,0,0,,That day, Renji chose some of the stronger\Npeople and set out from Bri-chan's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:36.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,The rest of us formed a party, but truthfully,\NI think there's a difference in our strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:41.00,fix,,0,0,0,,We spent eight silvers to join a guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:42.90,fix,,0,0,0,,Each have two silvers left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:48.65,fix,,0,0,0,,One silver equals one hundred coppers, so even if we\Nuse bare minimum, we'll only last about two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't want to camp out,\Nlet's spend carefully for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:59.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,In order to work in this world, you need to join a guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:02.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,Manato found this out for us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:09.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,As a party, we discussed and decided what roles\Nto take and sought out to join our respective guilds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You say you want to join my Thief Guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... that's what I came to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this is rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're choosing to be a Thief as your first job\Neven though you're just a Volunteer Soldier trainee?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you decide all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.80,0:14:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I talked with my party leader, Manato.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.10,0:14:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A-And I thought that someone like me\Ncould only make himself useful as a Thief—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:14:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! You're hurting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.65,0:15:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone realizes the value of having a Thief in your\Nparty once you're an experienced Volunteer Soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.95,0:15:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The first part of your training takes seven days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll go one-on-one with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:08.15,fix,,0,0,0,,Feel honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're reluctant, I can let someone else train you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, please! I insist!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to let you know, I'm strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll punish you if you can't keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go easy on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, should I call you "Teacher?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, you'll call me "Teacher?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That has a nice ring to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, er, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thieves get nicknames, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,After you complete your training,\NI'll give you a nice little nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Barbara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like we'll have a fun week.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:07.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,Teacher Barbara was always beautiful and sexy,\Nbut she was more sadistic than a sadist and was merciless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:10.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,Despite that, she gave me a nickname at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So my nickname is "Old Cat?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you always have the sleepy eyes of an elderly cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I was born like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:25.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,And so, I became a Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:27.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,Moguzo became a Warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:29.30,Italics,,0,0,0,,Ranta, a Dark Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:31.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,Yume, a Hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:33.75,Italics,,0,0,0,,Shihoru, a Magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:37.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,And Manato became a Priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not used these clothes yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.05,0:16:43.85,Italics,,0,0,0,,Frankly, I feel embarrassed wearing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Yume?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it just went down wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You should eat a little more slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:17:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why, but I always rush when I eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Master would always tell me,\N"Yume, it's bad if you don't eat slowly."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it not worded like that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe master said "Eat slowly"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you use a bow and arrow\Nproperly with a personality like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem super unfit to be a Hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Master did say that archery might be too tough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a bad shot, no matter how much I trained.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was dangerous yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.75,0:17:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I might have been thinking it'd be okay to hit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the one you almost hit, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Unforgivable. Especially since you're flat-chested.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Flat-chested?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I only forgive people like Shihoru\Nwho try to disguise their large boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.30,0:18:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,S— Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't fool me even if you hide them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can usually tell even if they're spread or flattened!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of skill is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a gift from the heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,An ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just because... I'm fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.65,0:18:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't seem fat to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My clothes just hide it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shihoru, are you the type of girl that other girls don't like?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls hate other girls who call themselves\Nfat even though they're not the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like guys and girls alike hate you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just guys and girls, the whole world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm world-class!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act like a saint, Haruhiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You were looking at Shihoru's chest earlier, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:18:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you dearly, with my mind's eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That just means you didn't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.25,0:19:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I really... am fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't—wait, it's not something to cry over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.50,0:19:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You clearly are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely see tears dripping down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry, Shihoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you aiming at me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'll miss this shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.95,0:19:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously! You're freakin' close!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You know Shihoru, you look skinny,\Nbut you're actually pretty soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't touch me... it's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.00,0:19:45.90,Alt,,0,0,0,,You smell good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:50.20,Alt,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you smell so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way... s-smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see how it feels to touch them...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:55.60,fix,,0,0,0,,Th-This is a feast for my eyes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:57.40,fix,,0,0,0,,Hey, you hear?!{Hey, are you okay with this?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:58.40,fix,,0,0,0,,Keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:20:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to break up the fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...but we should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.35,0:20:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be safe after sundown.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And it gets pitch-black.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Dangerous monsters will be out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's taking you guys so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You change gears just like that, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:17.35,fix,,0,0,0,,Naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a man who makes precise\Nchoices about time, place, and people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,People call me Master of Choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.90,0:20:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be King of the Choices!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three... four of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:20:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yume, you'll give us away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.20,0:21:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But, the Gobs are eating yummier food than mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.05,0:21:14.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,Day thirteen in Grimgar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:17.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,We didn't earn any money today either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:19.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,Our wallets are a little—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.10,0:21:22.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,No. Very empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.10,0:21:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.65,0:21:35.65,Italics,,0,0,0,,After today, tomorrow will come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:40.25,Italics,,0,0,0,,Maybe I've been taking that for granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.70,0:21:42.75,Italics,,0,0,0,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.05,0:21:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not... easy, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.90,0:21:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.05,0:21:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.30,0:21:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:13.45,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Repeating a yesterday filled with scrapes,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.45,0:22:18.25,op/ed,,0,0,0,,We clear the path to a hopeful tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.30,0:22:33.35,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I wonder what remains
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.35,0:22:36.55,op/ed,,0,0,0,,in both these tiny hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.55,0:22:42.90,op/ed,,0,0,0,,The voice I raised upwards scattered into the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.90,0:22:46.20,op/ed,,0,0,0,,The reality I've gamed is hazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.20,0:22:49.30,op/ed,,0,0,0,,and even if I can't see ahead of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:52.60,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I can keep moving forward on this long road
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:56.70,op/ed,,0,0,0,,if I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.70,0:23:02.95,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Connecting a bond covered in dust,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.95,0:23:09.30,op/ed,,0,0,0,,We join back to back in the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.30,0:23:15.75,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Repeating an answer full of mistakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.75,0:23:23.75,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I will reach out my hands to seek the light, again and again.
